\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 107. C. schousboei} Lange, {\i Vid. Meddel. Dansk Naturh. Foren. Kjøbenhavn}{\b  1861}: 85 (1861). Perennial. Stems 30-50 cm, erect, corymbosely branched. Leaves lanate to tomentose, grey; lower pinnatisect, with few, linear to lanceolate, mucronate segments. Capitula solitary. Involucre ovoid-oblong. Florets pink. Pappus about as long as achene.{\i  Grassland. • W. Spain, E.C. Portugal.} Hs Lu.
